{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v","text":"void"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"registerForPushNotificationsWithCompletion:"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"void (^)(NSString *, NSError *)","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:BFv(#*$objc(cs)NSString#*$objc(cs)NSError)"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"completion"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"completion","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Block called when registration completes, providing the push token or an error.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"Token is nil if registration failed or user denied permission."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This method combines system permission request with Pushwoosh server registration."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"The completion handler provides feedback on both operations, allowing you to:"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Update UI based on registration status","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Track registration analytics","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Handle errors gracefully with retry logic"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Sync push token with your backend server"}]}]}]},{"level":2,"text":"Example","anchor":"Example","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Handle registration in onboarding flow with analytics tracking:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["class OnboardingViewController: UIViewController {","","    func enableNotificationsTapped() {","        showLoadingState()","","        Pushwoosh.configure.registerForPushNotifications { [weak self] token, error in","            DispatchQueue.main.async {","                self?.hideLoadingState()","","                if let error = error {","                    Analytics.track(\"push_registration_failed\", properties: [","                        \"error\": error.localizedDescription","                    ])","                    self?.showRetryOption()","                    return","                }","","                if let token = token {","                    Analytics.track(\"push_registration_success\")","                    self?.syncTokenWithBackend(token)","                    self?.proceedToNextStep()","                } else {","                    Analytics.track(\"push_permission_denied\")","                    self?.showPermissionDeniedInfo()","                }","            }","        }","    }","","    private func syncTokenWithBackend(_ token: String) {","        APIClient.shared.updatePushToken(token) { result in","            if case .failure(let error) = result {","                Logger.error(\"Backend sync failed: \\(error)\")","            }","        }","    }","}"]}],"kind":"content"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/registerforpushnotificationswithcompletion:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"metadata":{"externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)registerForPushNotificationsWithCompletion:","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"roleHeading":"Type Method","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"registerForPushNotificationsWithCompletion:"}],"role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":